item.title: CoreUI PRO React.js Admin Template v5.0.0-rc.1 (Vite)
item.description: We’re excited to unveil the CoreUI PRO React.js Admin Template v5.0.0-rc.1, released on March 22, 2024. This version represents a significant leap forward, embracing the latest web development standards and technologies to provide an enhanced toolkit for building high-quality, responsive admin panels and dashboards.
